<HEADLINE>
<P>
ANR IS EXPANDING ITS ENERGY HOLDINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
HOUSTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANR Production Co. is purchasing additional interests in 374 producing oil and 
gas wells and a natural gas processing plant in the Altamont-Bluebell field of 
northeast Utah, the company said. 
</P>
<P>
A confidentiality agreement prevented ANR from disclosing the seller of the 
interests or the amount paid, said Jim Bailey, spokesman for Coastal Corp., 
ANR's parent firm. 
</P>
<P>
The transaction will increase ANR Production's average working interest in the 
374 wells from 28 to 42%, and its ownership in the Altamont Gas Processing 
Plant from 52.7% to 78.5%. 
</P>
